  <section id="biography">
  <h1>Julias Robert Oppenheimer</h1>
    <p>J. Robert Oppenheimer was born April 22, 1904 and his birthplace was Manhattan, New York, USA. He has lived in various places throughout his life, including California, New Mexico, and England, and he moved because his moves were elated to his work and academic pursuits. For example, he moved to California to work at the University of California, Berkeley, and later to New Mexico for his involvement in the Manhattan Project. He passed away February 18, 1967.</p>
